1
00:00:02,900 --> 00:00:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In class, there are lots of
different kinds of people.</i></font>

2
00:00:03,280 --> 00:00:04,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Dude, come on.</font>

3
00:00:06,450 --> 00:00:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those who can make others laugh...</i></font>

4
00:00:06,630 --> 00:00:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's that supposed to be?</font>

5
00:00:08,860 --> 00:00:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and those who make things lively.</i></font>

6
00:00:11,700 --> 00:00:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I...</i></font>

7
00:00:12,680 --> 00:00:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're gonna be a comedy duo,
you gotta start with an exchange journal!</font>

8
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:18,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would you think that?</font>

9
00:00:18,670 --> 00:00:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's obvious, isn't it?</font>

10
00:00:18,790 --> 00:00:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm the person holding back laughter off
to the side from the people having fun!</i></font>

11
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's no good. I'm going to laugh!</i></font>

12
00:00:25,380 --> 00:00:27,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Nishi-san's laughing!</font>

13
00:00:27,660 --> 00:00:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? For real?</font>

14
00:00:28,630 --> 00:00:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I odd for thinking that?</font>

15
00:00:30,130 --> 00:00:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's normal, right?</font>

16
00:00:31,180 --> 00:00:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it doesn't!</font>

17
00:00:31,850 --> 00:00:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But still!</font>

18
00:00:33,070 --> 00:00:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An exchange diary wouldn't work.</font>

19
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}First, you have to deepen
your bond as a duo.</font>

20
00:00:36,170 --> 00:00:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That's why you start an exchange diary!</font>

21
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so fast.</i></font>

22
00:00:37,570 --> 00:00:39,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The tempo of their
conversation is so fast!</i></font>

23
00:00:39,570 --> 00:00:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

24
00:00:41,270 --> 00:00:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you're putting
Nishi-san in a tough spot.</font>

25
00:00:43,810 --> 00:00:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

26
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry!</font>

27
00:00:45,430 --> 00:00:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no! It's not really...</font>

28
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I killed the mood.</i></font>

29
00:00:48,530 --> 00:00:50,280
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#8ef9f7"><font size="28">{\an7}EEEK</font></font></b></font>

30
00:00:52,530 --> 00:00:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was a shock!</i></font>

31
00:00:54,170 --> 00:00:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please don't suddenly bring me
into the conversation!</i></font>

32
00:00:56,530 --> 00:00:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It isn't that I want to join in!
I'm fine just listening!</i></font>

33
00:00:59,160 --> 00:01:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it's creepy that I was smiling
because of what I overheard. I'm sorry!</i></font>

34
00:01:02,790 --> 00:01:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nisshi, you really are shy
around people, aren't you?</font>

35
00:01:05,230 --> 00:01:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hon-chan, where have you been?</font>

36
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Borrowing this book from a friend.</font>

37
00:01:09,610 --> 00:01:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nisshi, if only you didn't get nervous,
you'd be able to talk normally.</font>

38
00:01:13,010 --> 00:01:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

39
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">comprehending what other people
are saying is one step.</font>

40
00:01:14,340 --> 00:01:16,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#39c4a4">FULL POWER</font></font></b></font>

41
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:19,430
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24">{\an8}<font color="#e16837">VISUALIZATION</font></font></b></font>

42
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thinking about how
to answer is one more step.</font>

43
00:01:19,470 --> 00:01:22,940
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#505ebb">PREPARING
\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hWORDS...</font></font></b></font>

44
00:01:19,670 --> 00:01:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And putting the things that popped
into my mind into words is another step.</font>

45
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:27,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lots of thoughts appear in my head,
but they never come out well in words.</font>

46
00:01:27,770 --> 00:01:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That hurdle is far too high for me!</font>

47
00:01:29,460 --> 00:01:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're super chatty now, though.</i></font>

48
00:01:30,730 --> 00:01:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't think it's something
you need to worry about, is it?</font>

49
00:01:33,390 --> 00:01:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say that earlier stuff was more about
enthusiasm than conversation anyway.</font>

50
00:01:37,270 --> 00:01:38,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, but...</font>

51
00:01:38,780 --> 00:01:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get even more nervous when it's a guy.</font>

52
00:01:41,250 --> 00:01:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whether they're guys or girls, they bleed
the same color when you stab them.</font>

53
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't stab anyone!</font>

54
00:01:47,130 --> 00:01:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Hon-chan! Lately, there's a boy
I keep thinking about.</font>

55
00:01:50,750 --> 00:01:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? When? You're not serious.</font>

56
00:01:52,130 --> 00:01:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is it? Who? Who?</font>

57
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, from the class next door.</font>

58
00:01:59,170 --> 00:02:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who?</i></font>

59
00:02:00,610 --> 00:02:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

60
00:02:01,390 --> 00:02:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The person who has library duty with you?</font>

61
00:02:03,770 --> 00:02:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

62
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said he doesn't talk much, didn't you?</font>

63
00:02:07,250 --> 00:02:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.
He isn't the type to talk much.</font>

64
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet...</font>

65
00:02:12,570 --> 00:02:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's nothing to do.</i></font>

66
00:02:21,110 --> 00:02:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An unexpected sort of student has arrived.</i></font>

67
00:02:25,350 --> 00:02:26,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

68
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san?</font>

69
00:02:28,210 --> 00:02:29,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They know each other?</i></font>

70
00:02:33,050 --> 00:02:35,800
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an7}<font size="24"><font color="#dd2d77">YAY YAY YAY</font></font></b></font>

71
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how I look at it,</font>

72
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:44,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">those two have a strange dynamic!</font>

73
00:02:44,830 --> 00:02:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's</i> why he's on your mind?</font>

74
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought that Tani-kun was like me,
so it was such a shock!</font>

75
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, not talking much
doesn't necessarily equal shyness.</font>

76
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She says impolite things so naturally.</i></font>

77
00:02:54,820 --> 00:02:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And also!</font>

78
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he wasn't just showing that off!</font>

79
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's also got delinquents idolizing him!</font>

80
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Right...</font>

81
00:03:01,110 --> 00:03:03,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wasn't scared of them
or just going along with them.</font>

82
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was talking to delinquents with
a fondly exasperated sort of attitude!</font>

83
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't say?</font>

84
00:03:08,670 --> 00:03:10,960
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24">{\an8}<font color="#0963b7">SIGH...</font></font></b></font>

85
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He seems like the protagonist
of a light novel.</i></font>

86
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:10,960
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24">{\an8}<font color="#0963b7">NOT
THIS
AGAIN...</font></font></b></font>

87
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He made amusing, 
perfectly timed comments,</font>

88
00:03:12,740 --> 00:03:14,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I could barely hold my laughter in.</font>

89
00:03:14,820 --> 00:03:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you were listening to people
and grinning to yourself again?</font>

90
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nisshi, what if you could just join in?</font>

91
00:03:20,580 --> 00:03:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not that I want to participate.</font>

92
00:03:22,210 --> 00:03:23,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say that...</font>

93
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if you can't stop thinking about him,</font>

94
00:03:25,250 --> 00:03:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are you jealous?</font>

95
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

96
00:03:27,090 --> 00:03:30,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like he's close to being in
the position you want to be in.</font>

97
00:03:30,850 --> 00:03:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

98
00:03:31,730 --> 00:03:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think that's it? That might be it.</font>

99
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that's probably it.</font>

100
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:53,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial">YOU AND I ARE POLAR OPPOSITES</font></b></font>

101
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's what it was.</i></font>

102
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:12,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've always thought that
I wanted to fix my shyness,</i></font>

103
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,920
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ffffff">WORDS
AND
THOUGHTS</font></font></font></b></font>

104
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,920
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="20"><font color="#84828c">COMMUNICATION
SKILLS</font></font></font></b></font>

105
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but the truth is that I wanted to be
included in that boisterous atmosphere!</i></font>

106
00:05:16,850 --> 00:05:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, but...</i></font>

107
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get that?</font>

108
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see now!</font>

109
00:05:21,470 --> 00:05:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perfect.</font>

110
00:05:22,090 --> 00:05:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're listening to him!</i></font>

111
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, Tani! Why don't you come
with us and we'll all go to TokyoU?</font>

112
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:27,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're jumping way too far ahead.</font>

113
00:05:31,850 --> 00:05:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He noticed.</i></font>

114
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do? He noticed that
I laughed just now!</i></font>

115
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he's looking this way.</i></font>

116
00:05:40,490 --> 00:05:46,070
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font color="#0ef2f0">ARGHHHHH...</font></b></font>

117
00:05:40,910 --> 00:05:44,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sorry! I'm sorry that I listened
without permission and laughed! I'm sorry!</i></font>

118
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please don't look at me!
It's scary! I'm sorry!</i></font>

119
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's totally impossible.</i></font>

120
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:49,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, for some reason,
I'm already terrified!</i></font>

121
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like people will think, "What?
Why are you laughing? And who are you?"</i></font>

122
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And they'd be entirely correct, too.</i></font>

123
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm really so very sorry.</i></font>

124
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nisshi, let's eat.</font>

125
00:06:00,230 --> 00:06:02,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nisshi, what's wrong?</font>

126
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After much consideration,</font>

127
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:10,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll refrain from aiming
too high and stick to my place.</font>

128
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What made you decide that?</font>

129
00:06:10,390 --> 00:06:11,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an4}<font size="16"><font color="#540079">AND REALLY,
YOU SHOULD LISTEN
TO THE LECTURE.</font></font></b></font>

130
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honda!</font>

131
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Yamada.</font>

132
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

133
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,900
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#0db6ea">BOW</font></font></b></font>

134
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:19,770
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#f7abf3">BOW</font></font></b></font>

135
00:06:19,150 --> 00:06:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Lo.</font>

136
00:06:20,780 --> 00:06:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was such a weird response!</i></font>

137
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honda, we're using that book
next period. Can I have it?</font>

138
00:06:25,330 --> 00:06:28,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry! I was going
to give it back later.</font>

139
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

140
00:06:28,780 --> 00:06:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hang on. Don't tell me that
 they know each other!</i></font>

141
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,710
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="24"><font color="#1eeab8">{\an7}STAAAAARE...</font></font></font></b></font>

142
00:06:35,910 --> 00:06:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you collecting those?</font>

143
00:06:37,220 --> 00:06:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

144
00:06:37,670 --> 00:06:39,590
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#ec5e97">BREAD FESTIVAL</font></font></b></font>

145
00:06:37,670 --> 00:06:39,590
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="12"><font color="#21b770"><font face="Arial">30 PTS IS GUARANTEED A PRIZE!</font></font></font></b></font>

146
00:06:39,590 --> 00:06:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was collecting them before, but it's
crazy hard to meet the requirements!</font>

147
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every day, bread!</font>

148
00:06:43,090 --> 00:06:44,010
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#fdffba">EVERY DAY,
BREAD</font></font></b></font>

149
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's... true.</font>

150
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:47,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you try for?</font>

151
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The yeti cushion.</font>

152
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wouldn't suit you.</font>

153
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah, but I want it.</font>

154
00:06:50,550 --> 00:06:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do?</i></font>

155
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Then, Yamada, do you have
yetis in your room right now?</font>

156
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is funny!</i></font>

157
00:06:53,610 --> 00:06:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah.</font>

158
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,350
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="24"><font color="#f7ffce">GASP</font></font></font></b></font>

159
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so sorry for laughing
at someone else's taste.</i></font>

160
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:59,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24">{\an4}<font color="#0c2f67">AAAAAAAA...</font></font></b></font>

161
00:06:59,980 --> 00:07:01,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Yamada!</font>

162
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,500
